title: Coquette's Bistro and Bakery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small 100% gluten/wheat/soy free cafe. Menu includes several clearly labeled vegan dishes, as well as several others that can be made vegan (including appetizers, salads, and entrees). Vegan brunch choices are also available on the weekends. The bakery part of the cafe serves vegan cupcakes, cakes and breads.
